- **Tantivy `f_dir_path`**: stored as a raw-tokenized string field; subtree filtering uses `RegexQuery` with `^regex::escape(prefix)`. `regex::escape` is called — so special chars in path names are handled. The `None | Some("" | "/")` no-filter shortcut is correct.
