---

### BUG 5 — `export` only exports 1 level [SERIOUS]

`execute.rs:1242–1338`

`export /` iterates `list_categories()` + `list_documents(cat_path)` per category — no subtree walk. Files in subdirectories are silently skipped.

`export <dir>` calls `list_documents(cat_path)` — same, only direct files.

Fix: recursive subtree walk using `list_directory` at each node; mirror directory structure to filesystem.

