### BUG 6 — `import` only imports 1 level [SERIOUS]

`execute.rs:1131–1238`

`import /` creates one category per top-level subdirectory and imports direct files only. Nested dirs and their files are marked `SKIPPED`.

`import <dir>` imports only files directly in the source dir; subdirs are `SKIPPED`.

